{"title":"矿山诗钞","authors":["巴牧"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":6,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"矿山诗钞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴牧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位煤矿电车司机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在煤烟滚滚的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你开车整整十年了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多熟悉的道路呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一天要走几遍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每当你拉响汽笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笛声也是热爱矿山的语言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位工程师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会场上掌声不断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要你讲讲成功的经验。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你却说得多么简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设计图上新加了一条线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这条线呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪亮着智慧的光采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间的波澜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位煤矿工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不必介绍你的名字了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我早就在光荣榜上看见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多想找机会同你长谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个夜晚又一个夜晚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从哪里说起呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天都看见你在超产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位青年工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你才二十岁光景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经有徒弟几十名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下的元老现在只有你了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你挑的担子可不轻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我还记得你用树皮盖房子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个简陋的工厂就在这山谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诞生。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}